column5: Raining like hell here. How's the BOG?
probably flooded. but its had ice for weeks, may be alright for january 1st when it opens.

As of x mas day,on lots of spots there was 7-8inches,and some places even more,but the usual spots near the river,and around by pine point are still not safe aparently !!!! but all this warm weather,man here in oshawa it hit 10degrees!!! so im hoping the bog will hold out???? i will get some more info in a few days....cheers
Curt you getting the ich too? I know i am i need to drill a few holes and start fishing befor i go nutts
I just had a family function and my wife's uncle who lives on the lake North of Wolf Run golf corse said he had 7" today with the rain.  It should be good come Jan. 01/09.
thanks guys. Jose, maybe we'll have to try to get out next weekend.  Curt

Talked to my friend who lives on the lake at veiw lake,and he said the lake is covered with lots of water,and wind is pliling the water up,and there is whitecaps on top of the ice !!!!   man there is acually waves on top !!!   but there still apperas to be lots of ice,he said you would need waders to check !!!! next update in a few days    cheers
